body_html:
It looks like you are using a TF quantized graph (made with the old graph transform tool) instead of a TFLite quantized graph.

Make sure you follow the quantization instructions here https://www.tensorflow.org/performance/quantization . We are working on some easier to use tools as well, for TensorFlow Lite quantization.

Closing due to inactivity, please create a new issue if the above technique doesn't work.
